{"tid":2515223,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【追車撚福音】快人一步　巴士追到！！","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:41:35.000Z","uid":85252,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f11287cfe2c0e2dedf58a3346573937aa4e0974c","tid":2515223,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過追車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打開個巴士Apps <br />\n全部都係Apps／廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/grab.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就享你好不容易完成考眼力遊戲<br />\n刪除個廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再望望架車仲有幾耐到站<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後發現得返最後一分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是你急起直追<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於！<br />\n成功目送架巴士離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家機會嚟啦！<br />\n介面清晣冇廣告<br />\nOpen source冇廣告嘅全新巴士 App <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chunlaw.github.io/hk-independent-bus-eta/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchunlaw.github.io%2Fhk-independent-bus-eta%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=c2edac84\" target=\"_blank\">https://chunlaw.github.io/hk-independent-bus-eta/</a><br />\n<br />\n脷伸，我覺得男人到左三十歲仲要依賴交通工具好可憐<br />\n但因為巴士廣告而追唔到巴士仲可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">琴晚見到有人係 App 台推唔郁:</span>o)<br />\n<span class=\"small\">怕變滄海遺珠</span>"},{"pid":"ac8da4fb134120bcfe7b1d8560cefc6a51eb067e","tid":2515223,"uid":33373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:15:51.000Z","msg":"網頁顏色唔得喎"},{"pid":"617bc542a944d328f3f656e6a0d534d8b8ea6171","tid":2515223,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:20:30.000Z","msg":"app呢"}